name: 12th Online Edition of International Conference on Preventive Medicine & Public Health
content: After successful accomplishment of our 11thEdition of International Conference on Preventive Medicine and Public Health on June 25, 2020\. We take colossal delight to welcome you at our new destination in Amsterdam, Netherlands from April 19-20, 2021 for our upcoming Event on 12thEdition of International Conference on Preventive Medicine and Public Health organized by Euroscicon Pte Ltd. (Preventive Medicine Conference 2020).
